             was indicted on 3 several indictments, viz. for <rs id="t17200303-34-off187" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17200303-34-off187" type="offenceCategory" value="miscellaneous"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17200303-34-off187" type="offenceSubcategory" value="other"></interp>
               enticing or endeavouring to perswade or solicit 
                     
                        <persName id="t17200303-34-victim230" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Shields 
                        <interp inst="t17200303-34-victim230" type="surname" value="Shields"></interp>
